extendedInfo.description: The game was created specifically for the youngest children. The game has a unique friendly interface. The child just press the button forward or back and travels to different countries. Along the way the car collects a variety of prizes, which will later allow the child to receive a new car and discover new country.Along the way a child does not meet the serious obstacles that will allow it to easily pass the whole journey from start to finish, bringing an enjoyment.In the garage child may choose cars, change their color and the wheels, allowing it to develop their creative abilities.Features:- friendly interface;- the absence of serious obstacles;- a special adaptation for children of the year.Keywords: cars, racing, for children, for kids, for boys, for girls, the best children's games, for pre-school age, race for kids, cars for children, children's games, educational games.
